- The integer array parameter `plants` must not be null.
- The length of the integer array parameter `plants` is greater than or equal to 1 and is less than or equal to 1000.
- All values in the integer array parameter `plants` are greater than or equal to 1 and are less than or equal to 1000000.
- The integer parameter `capacity` is greater than or equal to the maximum value in the integer array parameter `plants` and is less than or equal to 1000000000.
- The integer result is the number of steps needed to water all the plants.